{
  "page": "Walda Frey",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Walda Frey</b> is the name of several members of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Frey\" title=\"House Frey\">House Frey</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Twins\" title=\"Twins\">Crossing</a>.\nAs with the name <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey_(disambiguation)\" title=\"Walder Frey (disambiguation)\">Walder</a>, the name may be an attempt of the parents to please Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey\" title=\"Walder Frey\">Walder Frey</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey_(daughter_of_Walton)\" title=\"Walda Frey (daughter of Walton)\">Walda Frey</a>, also known as <i>Fair Walda</i>, the daughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Walton_Frey\" title=\"Walton Frey\">Walton Frey</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Deana_Hardyng\" title=\"Deana Hardyng\">Deana Hardyng</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey_(daughter_of_Merrett)\" title=\"Walda Frey (daughter of Merrett)\">Walda Frey</a>, also known as <i>Fat Walda</i>, second daughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Merrett_Frey\" title=\"Merrett Frey\">Merrett Frey</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Mariya_Darry\" title=\"Mariya Darry\">Mariya Darry</a>, third wife to <a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey_(daughter_of_Rhaegar)\" title=\"Walda Frey (daughter of Rhaegar)\">Walda Frey</a>, also known as <i>White Walda</i>, the daughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Frey\" title=\"Rhaegar Frey\">Rhaegar Frey</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jeyne_Beesbury\" title=\"Jeyne Beesbury\">Jeyne Beesbury</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey_(daughter_of_Edwyn)\" title=\"Walda Frey (daughter of Edwyn)\">Walda Frey</a>, the daughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Edwyn_Frey\" title=\"Edwyn Frey\">Edwyn Frey</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Janyce_Hunter\" title=\"Janyce Hunter\">Janyce Hunter</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Frey_(daughter_of_Lothar)\" title=\"Walda Frey (daughter of Lothar)\">Walda Frey</a>, second daughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Lothar_Frey\" title=\"Lothar Frey\">Lothar Frey</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Leonella_Lefford\" title=\"Leonella Lefford\">Leonella Lefford</a>.</li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Masculine_equivalent\">Masculine equivalent</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walda_Frey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Masculine equivalent\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Walder_Frey_(disambiguation)\" title=\"Walder Frey (disambiguation)\">Walder Frey (disambiguation)</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walda_Frey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Walda_Rivers_(disambiguation)\" title=\"Walda Rivers (disambiguation)\">Walda Rivers (disambiguation)</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Walda_Frey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot59.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_59\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 59\">Chapter 59</a>, Catelyn IX.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403131912\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.009 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.011 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 85/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8542/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 423/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 526/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    5.036      1 -total\n 73.99%    3.726      1 Template:Ref\n 46.80%    2.357      1 Template:Ref/core\n 24.38%    1.228      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:2914-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403131912 and revision id 282663\n -->\n",
